        "timestamp": "2018-08-30 12:13:15.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI wouldn't say that trigger criteria is too narrow - it just imposes directory structure on each functionality. Which actually already takes place but in different manner.\n\nIt makes sense to revert the change for now, however it's important to  resolve the issue in some way which probably needs some more discussion.",
